Class RemoveItem

java.lang.Object
  com.independentsoft.exchange.Item
      com.independentsoft.exchange.ResponseItem
          com.independentsoft.exchange.RemoveItem

public class RemoveItem
extends ResponseItem

Represents a response object that is used to remove a meeting item when a MeetingCancellation message is received.
